info.author: David M. Straub
info.description:
`CRunDec` is a C++ program developed by
Florian Herren and Matthias Steinhauser. This Python package
provides a thin wrapper around `CRunDec` generated with SWIG.
info.name: rundec
info.summary: A Python wrapper around the CRunDec package for the  running and decoupling of the strong coupling constant and quark masses
